{
  "stem": "24397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I liked to ride a bike, and whenever I had any money, I used to go to the park and rent a bicycle and ride home with it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And usually my dad would be at the window watching out for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that's-- I think that's what I spent most of my money, whenever I had any, on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It went on that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we used to have religious lessons in school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when, when the other children had their religious lessons, we had, we had ours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things were also very organized there that we went to school half day on Saturday, and in the afternoon, we went to special religious services in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to have a printed piece of card-- in fact, I have a, a Xerox copy of one of here-- that they used to give you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was relating to this week's portion that was being read in a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to bring that to school to show that we went to synagogue and had our instruction in this way.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, in the Orthodox environment it would have been very different for-- to begin with, they wouldn't have gone on Saturday morning to regular school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that's the way it was with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's a good question, but it's difficult to answer because these things didn't happen suddenly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't suddenly have Stormtroopers banging around and knocking people around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's subtle.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember we had a radio at home, and some of our neighbors who were very friendly with us didn't.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Hitler's speeches were being broadcasted, and they came in to our house and listened to the speeches.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
